<paragraph blockId="0.[1243,2123,694,924]" pageId="0" pageNumber="66">* Small-sized streamlined, semi-aquatic, egg-laying mammal, with distinctive pliable bill covered with naked moist skin, short limbs, broad flat tail, conspicuously webbed forefeet, and dense fine underfur and coarse overlaying guard hairs.</paragraph>
